Branch.ReportText: PI-RADS-1. Very low suspicion, clinically significant cancer is highly unlikely to be present.
PI-RADS-2. Low suspicion, clinically significant cancer is unlikely to be present.
PI-RADS-3. Intermediate suspicion, the presence of clinically significant cancer is equivocal.
PI-RADS-4. High suspicion, clinically significant cancer is likely to be present.
PI-RADS-5. Very high suspicion, clinically significant cancer is highly likely to be present.
